rules.name: Rules Text
rules.text:
{fontsize-10}When Probe Droid enters, target player reveals their hand.
Repair 3 {i}(When this creature dies, put three repair counters on it. At the beginning of your upkeep, remove a repair counter. Whenever the last is removed, you may cast it from your graveyard until end of turn.){/i}{/fontsize-10}
